0fishing%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELooking%20at%20the%20real%20danger%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20despite%20their%20efforts%2C%20fishermen%20continue%20to%20be%20scapegoated.%20When%20images%20of%20oil-slicked%20turtles%20emerge%20after%20environmental%20disasters%2C%20the%20media%20seeks%20quick%2C%20digestible%20outrage.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20wanted%20us%20to%20say%20the%20turtle%20died%20due%20to%20the%20oil%20spill%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arun%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20said%20no%20%E2%80%94%20it%20likely%20died%20earlier.%20The%20problem%20is%20deeper%3A%20trawling%2C%20pollution%2C%20unsustainable%20practices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Fengal%20cyclone%20in%20November%202024%2C%20Payalam%20was%20left%20grappling%20with%20an%20overwhelming%20amount%20of%20plastic%20waste%20along%20the%20shore.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20pollution%20near%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F417010%2Fsstcn-chennai-olive-ridley-conservation-decades-student-initiative-hatchery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebroken%20bridge%20in%20Adyar%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20so%20severe%20that%20many%20fish%20perished%2C%E2%80%9D%20Palayam%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20such%20conditions%2C%20how%20can%20we%20expect%20the%20turtles%20to%20survive%2C%20let%20alone%20lay%20their%20eggs%20peacefully%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asks%2C%20his%20voice%20filled%20with%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-09T164257.577-1746789201.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22trash%20and%20dead%20fishes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-09T164257.577-1746789201.jpg%201