ollege%20of%20Cardinals%20on%20Saturday%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20papal%20conclave.%20In%20his%20speech%2C%20the%20new%20pope%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Esaid%20artificial%20intelligence%20influenced%20his%20decision%20to%20take%20the%20name%20Leo%20XIV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSensing%20myself%20called%20to%20continue%20in%20this%20same%20path%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20take%20the%20name%20Leo%20XIV.%20There%20are%20different%20reasons%20for%20this%2C%20but%20mainly%20because%20Pope%20Leo%20XIII%20in%20his%20historic%20Encyclical%20'Rerum%20Novarum'%20addressed%20the%20social%20question%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20first%20great%20industrial%20revolution%2C%26quot%3B%20Leo%20XIV%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20our%20own%20day%2C%20the%20Church%20offers%20to%20everyone%20the%20treasury%20of%20her%20social%20teaching%20in%20response%20to%20another%20industrial%20revolution%20and%20to%20developments%20in%20the%20field%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20that%20pose%20new%20challenges%20for%20the%20defence%20of%20human%20dignity%2C%20justice%2C%20and%20labor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaturday's%20address%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20the%20Catholic%20Church%20has%20reflected%20on%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.vatican.va%2Fcontent%2Fsalastampa%2Fit%2Fbollettino%2Fpubblico%2F2025%2F01%2F28%2F0083%2F01166.html%23ing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Holy%20See%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20governing%20body%20of%20the%20Catholic%20Church%2C%20published%20a%20lengthy%20note%20on%20the%20relationship%20between%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20human%20intelligence.%20The%20note%20said%20the%20Catholic%20Church%20%26quot%3Bencourages%20the%20advancement%20of%20science%2C%20technology%2C%20the%20arts%2C%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20human%20endeavor%26quot%3B%20but%20sought%20to%20address%20the%20%26quot%3Banthropological%20and%20ethical%20challenges%20raised%20by%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20issues%20that%20are%20particularly%20significant%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20goals%20of%20this%20technology%20is%20to%20imitate%20the%20human%20intelligence%20that%20designed%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeo%20XIV's%20predecessor%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpope-francis-dead-obituary-2025-4%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPope%2520Francis%2520died%2520on%2520April%2Cbeen%2520involved%2520in%2520religious%2520leadership.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPope%20Francis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20discussed%20AI%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vatican.va%2Fcontent%2Ffrancesco%2Fen%2Fmessages%2Fcommunications%2Fdocuments%2F20240124-messaggio-comunicazioni-sociali.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJanuary%202024%20message%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20by%20the%20Holy%20See.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rapid%20spread%20of%20astonishing%20innovations%2C%20whose%20workings%20and%20potential%20are%20beyond%20the%20ability%20of%20most%20of%20us%20to%20understand%20and%20appreciate%2C%20has%20proven%20both%20exciting%20and%20disorienting%2C%26quot%3B%20Pope%20Francis%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20leads%20inevitably%20to%20deeper%20questions%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20human%20beings%2C%20our%20distinctiveness%20and%20the%20future%20of%20the%20species%20homo%20sapiens%20in%20the%20age%20of%20artificial%20intelligence.%20How%20can%20we%20remain%20fully%20human%20and%20guide%20this%20cultural%20transformation%20to%20serve%20a%20good%20purpose%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPope%20Francis%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20this%20time%20in%20history%2C%20which%20risks%20becoming%20rich%20in%20technology%20and%20poor%20in%20humanity%2C%20our%20reflections%20must%20begin%20with%20the%20human%20heart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpope-leo-xiv-ai-artificial-intelligence-speech-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746986874000%2