gy%2C%20and%20increasing%20independence.%20I'd%20love%20to%20do%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhonor-mom-anniversary-death-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esomething%20meaningful%20on%20Mother's%20Day%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Yet%2C%20the%20thought%20of%20orchestrating%20a%20traditional%20celebration%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20that%20often%20involves%20a%20partner's%20thoughtful%20planning%20and%20execution%20%E2%80%94%20feels%20like%20adding%20another%20task%20onto%20my%20already%20overflowing%20plate.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20working%20single%20mom%2C%20the%20mental%20and%20emotional%20labor%20of%20planning%2C%20deciding%2C%20preparing%2C%20arranging%2C%20and%20managing%20is%20never-ending.%20Adding%20the%20pressure%20of%20creating%20a%20Pinterest-worthy%20Mother's%20Day%20feels%20less%20like%20a%20celebration%20and%20more%20like%20another%20%26quot%3Bto-do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8bf5b62-f010-4ae5-a085-f32ef3e0249b%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20dropping%20my%20toddler%20off%20with%20my%20mom%20for%20a%20day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20considered%20not%20making%20any%20plans%20and%20letting%20the%20day%20once%20again%20pass%20without%20notice%2C%20but%20I%20also%20feel%20that%20this%20incredible%20journey%20of%20motherhood%20deserves%20special%20recognition.%20I%20decided%20to%20split%20the%20weekend%20into%20two%20parts.%20On%20the%20Friday%20before%20Mother's%20Day%2C%20I'm%20dropping%20Via%20off%20with%20my%20mom%20for%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoddler-sleep-regression-checke-into-a-hotel-to-sleep-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esleep-cation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Every%20time%20I%20catch%20up%20on%20rest%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20the%20best%20version%20of%20myself%3B%20the%20best%20gift%20I%20could%2