ers%20who%20feel%20they%20rarely%20have%20time%20in%20their%20day-to-day%20life%20to%20enjoy%20books%20without%20getting%20pulled%20into%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c93566e8-69eb-48f2-8f20-eb2e0b4d3e69%5C%22%3E3.%20Bare%20witness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20look%20up%20at%20sky%20with%20glasses%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e82c23fe8d3928365823e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETravel%20to%20view%20solar%20eclipses%20is%20booming%2C%20including%20among%20the%20wealthy.%3Cp%3ERONALDO%20SCHEMIDT%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETraveling%20for%20natural%20phenomena%20is%20another%20trend%20among%20Black%20Tomato%20clients%2C%20with%20the%20company%20increasingly%20planning%20trips%20around%20natural%20events%20that%20could%20be%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20opportunity%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20years%20ago%20the%20company%20built%20bespoke%20camps%20in%20the%20mountains%20of%20Patagonia%20so%20its%20clients%20could%20witness%20the%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20in%20luxury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraveling%20to%20witness%20natural%20phenomena%20like%20eclipses%2C%20the%20northern%20lights%2C%20or%20animal%20migrations%20could%20be%20especially%20appealing%20to%20the%20wealthy%20because%20it's%20likely%20to%20be%20very%20different%20from%20their%20daily%20life%2C%20Marchant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20clients%20live%20in%20LA%2C%20so%20traveling%20somewhere%20with%20a%20gorgeous%20villa%2C%20fancy%20pool%2C%20and%20nice%20weather%20is%20less%20likely%20to%20be%20appealing%20to%20them%20since%20it's%20what%20they%20already%20have%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225db122fa-f0cf-4eff-9602-7e9a0b413fbb%5C%22%3E4.%20Travel%20as%20therapy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20major%20trend%20in%20luxury%20travel%20Marchant%20said%20he's