20state%2C%20adapting%20to%20each%20situation%20%E2%80%94%20and%20each%20kid%20%E2%80%94%20as%20necessary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d75bd74-e86d-4f49-9ed7-df33e85e4a51%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20works%20for%20one%20child%20doesn't%20necessarily%20work%20for%20another%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20early%20years%2C%20when%20I%20still%20thought%20there%20was%20one%20%26quot%3Bright%26quot%3B%20way%20to%20do%20things%2C%20my%20first%20baby%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20a%20parenting%20prodigy.%20Early%20on%2C%20she%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbedtime-cuddles-kids-sleep-open-conversations-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esleeping%20through%20the%20night%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20eating%20well%2C%20and%20was%20just%20generally%20easygoing.%20Naturally%2C%20I%20chalked%20up%20this%20temperament%20to%20my%20diligent%20following%20of%20expert%20advice%20and%20congratulated%20myself%20on%20learning%20how%20to%20be%20an%20excellent%20mother.%20Then%20my%20second%20baby%20arrived%20and%20blew%20that%20theory%20to%20pieces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20worked%20for%20my%20first%20didn't%20work%20at%20all%20for%20my%20second.%20Techniques%20I'd%20previously%20sworn%20by%2C%20like%20Dr.%20Harvey%20Karp's%20%26quot%3B5%20S's%26quot%3B%20for%20soothing%20babies%2C%20only%20left%20my%20new%20baby%20shrieking%20louder.%20And%20nothing%20humbles%20you%20faster%20than%20an%20inconsolable%20newborn%20who%20refuses%20to%20be%20soothed%20by%20a%20checklist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20I%20went%20back%20to%20the%20drawing%20board%2C%20fumbling%20my%20way%20through%20the%20early%20days%20of%20parenting%20and%20following%20my%20son's%20cues%20to%20learn%20what%20settled%20him%20instead.%20It%20was%20deflating%2C%20but%20it%20also%20taught%20me%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flessons-ive-learned-from-parenting-four-teens-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egreat%20lesson%20in%20parenting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20early%20on%3A%20no%20two%20children%20are%20alike%2C%20and%20parenting%20strategies%20need%20to%20bend%20with%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20with%20two%20of%20her%20kids%20sitting%20on%20a%20beach%20by%20colorful%20picnic%20tables.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681a35883fe8d3928365119d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20has%20learned%20that%20flexible%20parenting%20works%20best%20with%20her.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Tiffany%20Nieslanik%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c42c821d-40cd-492a-946a-a103e8af0716%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFlexibility%20allows%20me%20to%20be%20a%20more%20responsive%20parent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%20time%20our%20third%20child%20was%20born%2C%20I%20had%20zero%20expectations.%20I%20had%20a%20full%20toolbelt%20of%20ideas%2C%20thanks%20to%20all%20that%20reading%20I%20had%20done%20and%20the%20five%20years%20of%20parenting%20experience%20I%20had%20gained%2C%20but%20no%20illusions%20that%20any%20one%20approach%20would%20work%20universally.%20This%20flexibility%20made%20me%20a%20calmer%2C%20more%20responsive%20parent.%20And%20not%20just%20during%20the%20baby%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20our%20kids%20grew%2C%20it%20became%20even%20more%20obvious%20that%20each%20one%20handled%20the%20world%20differently.%20I%20had%20also%20learned%20that%2C%20just%20like%20soothing%20techniques%20needed%20to%20vary%2C%20so%20does%20emotional%20support.%20One%20of%20our%20children%20wants%20a%20quiet%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fson-says-best-parenting-technique-giving-time-outs-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%