20dust.%20But%20through%20solar%20drying%2C%20the%20produce%20will%20be%20safe.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20cheese%2C%20Tsetan%20plans%20to%20mimic%20the%20process%20for%20wild%20herbs%20like%20caraway%20and%20nettle%2C%20and%20the%20Halman%20apricots%20%E2%80%94%20a%20substitute%20for%20sugar%20in%20Siachen%20Naturals%E2%80%99%20sweet%20barley%20porridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENettle%20leaves%20(%3Cem%3Ezasthot%3C%2Fem%3E)%20are%20considered%20a%20rich%20source%20of%20iron%20and%20calcium.%20Native%20to%20the%20highlands%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20herb%E2%80%99s%20status%20is%20relatively%20reverential.%20The%20saint%20Milarepa%2C%20who%20exiled%20himself%20to%20the%20mountains%20to%20meditate%2C%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20relied%20on%20nettle%20plants%20exclusively%20for%20nourishment.%20This%20is%20why%2C%20Tsetan%20explains%2C%20in%20the%20local%20parlance%2C%20nettle%20soup%20is%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Milarepa%E2%80%99s%20soup%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fmothers-of-the-better-india-11-1746609268.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20wild%20nettle%20soup%20is%20one%20of%20the%20cult%20classics%20on%20the%20Siachen%20Naturals%20menu%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fmothers-of-the-better-india-11-1746609268.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fmothers-of-the-better-india-11-1746609268-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fmothers-of-the-better-india-11-1746609268-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fmothers-of-the-better-india-11-1746609268-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterin